好。勿花無謂金錢。"},{"pid":"091764bd80c93ef6ae59a8d5d771fc7481ac8343","tid":2157993,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"我唔識 <br />\n大家推下post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}